---
title: "WorkflowRouter.onReport (Payment Abstraction V2)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_forwarder: check caller
    q_check_forwarder --> q_error_forwarder: caller lacks FORWARDER_ROLE
    q_error_forwarder --> [*]: revert "access denied"
    q_check_forwarder --> q_decode: caller has FORWARDER_ROLE

    q_decode --> q_extract: decode (workflowId, payload)
    q_extract --> q_route: lookup target contract and function by workflowId

    q_route --> q_auction_perform: workflowId == auctionManager
    q_route --> q_auction_transmit: workflowId == priceManager
    q_route --> q_bidder_bid: workflowId == auctionBidder
    q_route --> q_error_unknown: workflowId not registered

    q_auction_perform --> [*]: call auction.performUpkeep(payload)
    q_auction_transmit --> [*]: call auction.transmit(payload)
    q_bidder_bid --> [*]: call auctionBidder.bid(payload)
    q_error_unknown --> [*]: revert "unknown workflow"

    note right of q_route
        INV-028: WorkflowRouter validates workflowId before routing
        INV-029: only FORWARDER_ROLE (CRE forwarder) can call onReport
        INV-030: routing is deterministic - one workflowId maps to one target
    end note
